    <string name="terms_h1">1. 📄 Acceptance of terms</string>
    <string name="terms_p1">By using Travel Planner you accept these terms and conditions. If you do not agree with any of these conditions, you must not use the application.</string>
    <string name="terms_h2">2. 🔐 Privacy and data</string>
    <string name="terms_p2">Travel Planner collects only the data necessary for the app to function: username, saved destinations, and itineraries. We do not share your data with third parties without your explicit consent.</string>
    <string name="terms_h3">3. 🛠️ Application usage</string>
    <string name="terms_p3">Travel Planner is a personal planning tool. The information shown is purely orientational. Always verify facts with official providers before finalizing reservations.</string>
    <string name="terms_h4">4. 🌐 Third-party services</string>
    <string name="terms_p4">The application might integrate external services like Google Maps or flight APIs. The use of these services is bound by their own privacy policies and usage terms.</string>
